						               													<description>Meeple Company is a strategic worker placement boardgame in which you will have to play your meeples wisely to accomplish your company's three objectives.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;You will be able to choose between four types of companies: the laboratory, the toy factory, the robotics company and the chocolate factory. The objectives to be achieved will be the following:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;To have a single meeple of your presidency.&amp;#10;To have the highest number of meeples in your main department&amp;#10;To have no prohibited meeples in your company.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;To achieve this, you will be able to perform 4 different actions:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Hire: you choose a meeple from those located in the center of the table and place it in your Hall.&amp;#10;Move: you choose one of your meeples and send it to a rival's Hall.&amp;#10;Send to a Congress: you choose a meeple from your work area or from the center of the table and everyone must remove a meeple of that color from their company.&amp;#10;Close: you close your company for this day, you will not be able to perform any more actions or receive any more meeple. The meeples of your Hall go to your work area.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
